I say why sure  ,but she had to ask the manager So off she went to ask and when she returned, she says ,SIR. I said ME,Am I geting old or what.LOL She says please grab the 40 dollar sales tag there and bring it to me. I couldnt grab that tag fast enough. Bring it up to her,she scans the tag and to me and the mrs surprise, it comes up 29 bucks.   She says nothing,I say SWEET, and off I go with my new spring turkey suit for 2009.
